widgets_values:
1.Find frame to replace , remember the number.
2.Edit it and add it to the list of images.
3.Add before-number-after  numbers to "Wan Video VACE Frame Replace" (number from step 1)

In example 6-35-6  frame 35 will be replaced , with 6 buffer frames for transition.
Multiple frames can be replaced. Adding another line of numbers after etc.
City drone footage , spaceship appears from the right side , spaceship flies from one side to another and crashes offscreen as camera slowly moves through the city.
